OOC: I'm gonna say yeah, because I am not sure what JP did with him when
he first brought him back. Kslawdogg do you know? Yeah it is moding not
to accept dammage, but I am accepting dammage, I got hit by your stun
gun, and Megatron's main arm dosent work. Plus I've already accepted
lots of dammage this fight, from KSLawdogg (could you respond to
Spasstik's attacks big guy:) and Prowl. Plus I am going somewhere with
this.

BIC:

Megatron did not let any of this faze him. He was suprised this was not
a Maximal. "Never call me a Predacon." Megatron said through clenched
teeth. He strained to raise his cannon arm again, aiming at Mutate. With
a quivering strain, he aimed at the mutated creature.
----------------------------------------------------------------------

Rampage rode over the terrain, his treads grinding the earth. He looked
up at the two hovering robots. "Ahhh it is you my friend." He whispered,
when he then noticed the one robot aiming at him. "It can't be,
Megatron, ho ho ho, we are going to have fun here. HERE ARE SOME IRON
RATIONS." he screamed as his gattling gun barrel turned, then fired off
a rocket at the Decepticon leader. The shell screamed off towards the
Decepticon leader, leaving a trail of smoke as it slammed into
Megatron's back, tearing a hole into his armor, and sending him
plummeting to the ground.
